16:44.032 --> 16:46.265
TV commercial. Highly targeted.

16:46.317 --> 16:50.103
Let me tell you, at Sandpiper,
the trains run on time.

16:50.155 --> 16:52.155
Mussolini would be proud.

16:52.190 --> 16:55.608
