same exact schedule.

16:55.660 --> 16:57.443
10:00 a.m., water aerobics.

16:57.495 --> 16:59.112
2:00 p.m., line dancing.

16:59.164 --> 17:00.413
So on and so forth.

17:00.448 --> 17:02.949
