to 4:00 p.m. free.

17:03.001 --> 17:04.951
Why? "Murder, She Wrote."

17:06.087 --> 17:07.703
It's been in syndication
since like the 1850s,

17:07.704 --> 17:09.789
and let me tell you,
when that thing comes on,

17:09.840 --> 17:12.592
it draws the blue-hairs
like moths to a bug zapper.

17:13.762 --> 17:16.679
3:14 p.m., end of the first-act cliffhanger,

17:16.714 --> 17:19.098
