worked in the highly lucrative,

20:06.294 --> 20:08.678
creatively rewarding field of advertising,

20:08.713 --> 20:10.847
and tonight, we join them.

20:10.882 --> 20:13.266
This is heady stuff, right?

20:13.301 --> 20:15.768
Okay. So, pay attention.

20:15.803 --> 20:19.355
We open on granny, and she is rocking.

20:19.390 --> 20:25.728
