- It's true.

20:45.383 --> 20:46.999
Okay, no dolly.

20:47.001 --> 20:49.502
Um...

20:49.504 --> 20:51.721
We will improvise, then.

20:51.756 --> 20:53.172
Stay with me.

20:53.174 --> 20:54.674
She's rocking.

20:54.726 --> 20:55.925
She's shivering.

20:58.513 --> 21:02.148
She's clutching at a tattered shawl.

21:04.452 --> 21:07.687
They turned the heat off on her,
