Are you all right?

25:24.078 --> 25:25.277
Let me show you.

25:27.365 --> 25:30.499
It's up... it's up there.

25:30.535 --> 25:32.001
You see it?

25:32.036 --> 25:34.670
It's right up there.

25:34.705 --> 25:35.921
You see that?

25:35.957 --> 25:38.123
You see the shape of it?

25:38.176 --> 25:40.176
You do see it, right?

25:40.211 --> 25:41.510
I... I see it.

25:41.546 --> 25:44.964
What time did you hear the shots?

25:44.966 --> 25:46.849
2:13 this morning.

25:46.884 --> 25:49.268
I looked at the clock. It was three of them.

25:49.303 --> 25:51.020
It was exactly like last time.

25:51.055 --> 25:52.688
And you didn't call the police. Or did you?

25:52.723 --> 25:54.306
No, I...

25:54.308 --> 25:57.059
What's the point?

25:58.863 --> 26:02.031
Uh... I'm thinking outside the box, but...

26:02.066 --> 26:05.818
you think maybe it's possible
that you dreamed it?

26:05.870 --> 26:07.486
It happens sometimes.

26:07.538 --> 26:09.205
I didn't dream it, Mike.

26:09.240 --> 26:11.790
Because I didn't sleep a wink last night.

26:11.826 --> 26:13.492
That came from a bullet.

26:13.544 --> 26:15.044
I mean, it must have.

26:15.079 --> 26:16.795
It wasn't there before last night.

26:16.831 --> 26:18.714
I promise you that, and I don't know...

26:18.749 --> 26:19.915
Okay.

26:19.967 --> 26:23.903
Okay. Jesus...

26:23.938 --> 26:25.221
I mean, I was here.

26:25.256 --> 26:27.006
I was here, and you weren't.

26:27.008 --> 26:28.724
I believe you.

26:30.978 --> 26:32.711
I believe you.

26:36.851 --> 26:39.852
All right. That's it.

26:39.854 --> 26:43.355
We're getting you and Kaylee
out of this house.

26:43.357 --> 26:46.408
End of story.

27:05.262 --> 27:07.196
You ever wonder about these things?

27:07.231 --> 27:08.531
What things?

27:08.566 --> 27:10.866
This. Like, what's the story with these?

27:10.902 --> 27:12.785
Who was it who first said,

27:12.820 --> 27:15.237
"Hey, I know... big bowl of balls."

27:15.239 --> 27:18.140
I don't know. They came with the place.

27:18.175 --> 27:19.408
No shit.

27:19.460 --> 27:21.877
They're in every corporate
apartment in the world.

27:21.913 --> 27:23.879
They're like the Gideon Bible.

27:23.915 --> 27:26.215
Hey, don't be jealous
of my big bowl of balls.

27:26.250 --> 27:27.466
It's unbecoming.

27:27.501 --> 27:30.502
Why do they all have to have empty vases?

27:30.555 --> 27:32.154
Well, it's the law.

27:32.189 --> 27:35.007
Plus, it's a metaphor.

27:35.059 --> 27:36.175
I got to say,

27:36.227 --> 27:38.227
I will miss the nail salon's
vibrating chairs.

27:38.262 --> 27:39.311
Well, for you,

27:39.347 --> 27:41.847
I can make any chair in this place vibrate.

27:43.017 --> 27:45.100
You ready for this?

27:46.487 --> 27:48.354
