27:48.406 --> 27:49.605
You're 86 years old.

27:49.607 --> 27:51.824
You're a resident of Sandpiper,
Colorado Springs.

27:51.859 --> 27:54.360
You just finished your
afternoon snack, lime Jell-O.

27:54.412 --> 27:55.678
Lime, got it.

27:55.713 --> 27:56.879
You're in the dayroom,

27:56.914 --> 27:58.847
