27:58.883 --> 27:59.949
What's this?

27:59.984 --> 28:01.517
There's been another murder in Cabot Cove?

28:01.552 --> 28:02.518
No!

28:02.553 --> 28:03.702
Yes.

28:03.754 --> 28:05.421
The sheriff is in over his head,
and once again,

28:05.456 --> 28:07.256
Jessica Fletcher has to put aside

28:07.291 --> 28:10.092
the novel she's been writing
and assist law enforcement.

28:10.127 --> 28:11.293
Shocker!

28:11.345 --> 28:15.631
The killer left behind
a cryptogram... and commercial.

28:24.191 --> 28:27.726
My husband and I scrimped
and saved for so many years.

28:27.778 --> 28:30.229
We did our best to build a nest egg

28:30.281 --> 28:33.315
so that we wouldn't be a burden
to our family.

28:33.367 --> 28:37.319
After Ronald passed, I moved to
an assisted-living facility...

28:37.371 --> 28:38.654
a nice place.

28:38.706 --> 28:41.790
