37:02.088 --> 37:03.137
What's the job?

37:03.172 --> 37:05.756
I asked. Guy wouldn't tell me.

37:05.758 --> 37:08.926
But whatever it is, it's serious money.

37:08.928 --> 37:10.177
And the guy...

37:10.229 --> 37:14.265
he specifically asked for you.

37:14.317 --> 37:17.835
And who's the guy?

37:17.870 --> 37:18.969
I can't hold it, sir.

37:19.005 --> 37:20.771
No control on the planes, Captain.

37:20.807 --> 37:22.239
We're going down and fast.

37:22.275 --> 37:24.108
"We're going down and fast."

37:24.143 --> 37:25.142
Check this out.

37:25.178 --> 37:26.377
This is a good part.

37:26.412 --> 37:28.412
So, do they all die? Tell me that much.

37:28.448 --> 37:29.980
Shh, shh, shh, shh!

37:30.016 --> 37:33.384
Does Rock Hudson run 'em into an iceberg?

37:35.455 --> 37:39.857
Is this... Before or after
he did "McMillan & Wife"?

37:39.892 --> 37:42.927
Shut up. Watch the movie.

37:45.364 --> 37:46.964
What is this weird fascination you have

37:46.999 --> 37:50.101
with stories of men trapped
on the North Pole?

37:50.136 --> 37:52.970
"Ice Station Zebra" is on the North Pole.

37:52.972 --> 37:54.155
"The Thing" takes place on the South Pole.

37:54.159 --> 37:56.242
They literally could not
be any more different.

37:56.244 --> 37:58.211
My dad loves this one.

37:58.246 --> 38:00.496
Yeah, him and Howard Hughes.

38:00.548 --> 38:02.749
I know, right?

38:02.801 --> 38:05.752
Can't get two finer reviews than that.

38:05.754 --> 38:07.804
How much pressure's left
in the air banks?

38:07.839 --> 38:09.756
Down 800 pounds, sir.

38:09.758 --> 38:13.226
Secure after group blow.

38:16.514 --> 38:18.598
Mnh-mnh!

38:18.650 --> 38:19.982
It's the boss.

38:20.018 --> 38:21.267
At this hour?

38:21.319 --> 38:22.351
Yeah.

38:22.404 --> 38:25.571
It's never too late for congratulations.

38:27.358 --> 38:30.777
Cliff, Jesus, you're still at the office?

38:30.829 --> 38:33.362
You ran a commercial?

38:33.415 --> 38:35.531
Yeah, and, oh, my God,

38:35.583 --> 38:37.366
let me tell you, the response has been...

38:37.419 --> 38:39.869
You ran a commercial
without ever showing it to me,

38:39.921 --> 38:41.537
without first consulting me and my partners.

38:41.589 --> 38:43.840
Did you actually think that was gonna fly?!

38:43.875 --> 38:46.259
I was planning on telling you
in the morning.

38:46.294 --> 38:47.710
The day after it aired?!

38:47.762 --> 38:51.047
I only ran it once,
just in one small market.

38:51.099 --> 38:52.882
It was kind of an experiment, all right?

38:52.934 --> 38:54.767
Kind of under the radar.

38:54.803 --> 38:56.185
And in all fairness,

38:56.221 --> 38:59.522
you did tell me client outreach
was my department.

38:59.557 --> 39:01.057
Don't be disingenuous.

39:01.109 --> 39:05.394
This commercial... I take it
my firm's name is mentioned?

39:05.447 --> 39:07.980
Yes. Yeah.

39:08.032 --> 39:09.065
Jesus...

39:09.117 --> 39:10.650
Howard said you were a little eccentric.

39:10.702 --> 39:13.052
He didn't tell me
you were a goddamn arsonist!

39:13.087 --> 39:16.489
Cliff, to be fair, I don't think, uh...

39:18.037 --> 39:19.449
Uh...

39:19.755 --> 39:20.642
I apologize if there was any misreading

39:20.712 --> 39:23.329
of the situation on my part,

39:23.381 --> 39:25.498
but there's a very positive headline here.

39:25.550 --> 39:28.417
We got 103 phone calls today,

39:28.470 --> 39:30.419
off a measly $700 ad buy.

39:30.472 --> 39:33.089
Now that kind of return
on investment you can't g...

39:33.141 --> 39:35.842
Tomorrow morning, 8:00,
my office, with the partners,

39:35.894 --> 39:37.477
and we want to see this thing.

39:37.512 --> 39:40.880
Cliff, when you see this, I know you'll...

39:45.453 --> 39:47.403
Yeah, Cliff.

39:48.773 --> 39:49.822
Thank you.

39:49.858 --> 39:51.524
Yeah, you, too.

39:51.576 --> 39:52.525
Okay.

39:52.577 --> 39:55.695
See ya.

39:55.747 --> 39:57.613
Golden boy.

39:57.665 --> 39:59.365
That's me.

40:05.039 --> 40:06.539
So, what'd I miss?

40:06.541 --> 40:08.207
Anything blow up yet?

41:11.606 --> 41:14.106
Feeling cautious?

41:15.860 --> 41:19.412
You gonna tell me what we're doing here?

41:19.647 --> 41:21.581
I've got a problem.

41:21.616 --> 41:23.866
- Okay.
- This problem...

41:23.918 --> 41:26.619
I can't solve it myself.

41:26.621 --> 41:30.506
This problem... is it a who or a what?

41:32.093 --> 41:34.293
There's a guy.

41:36.297 --> 41:39.849
I need him to go away.

